Did you buy something during Black Friday 2018? What did you buy, and how much did you spend? We have launched our Black Friday 2018 Spending and Purchases Survey which takes a look at what went down on the sales weekend. The survey will only take 1 minute to complete and you will provide valuable insight into local shopping trends. There is also a prize giveaway which you can enter by taking part in the survey. Up for grabs is a 20,000mAh powerbank and a Bluetooth tracker tag. The results of the survey will be published in articles on MyBroadband will make for interesting reading.